{{Quote|Jedi business, go back to your drinks.|Anakin Skywalker, to Dixon Just and other clubgoers|audio=Anakin-JediBusiness-AOTC.flac|<ref name="AoTC" />}}
'''Dixon Just''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]]<ref name="AoTC" /> who was a frequent patron of<ref name="CSWE" /> the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]<ref name="TVD">''[[Star Wars: Attack of the Clones: The Visual Dictionary]]''</ref> [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|underworld]] in the [[Standard year/Legends|years]] before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. He was often seen in the company of his friends [[Zey Nep]], [[Artuo Pratuhr]], and [[Civ Sila]].<ref name="CSWE" /> During a [[Local day/Legends|night]]<ref name="AoTC" /> in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]],<ref name="NEC">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]'' dates the events of {{Film|II}} to [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].</ref> Just, alongside Nep, Pratuhr, and Sila, visited the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]],<ref name="AoTC" /> a [[Nightclub/Legends|nightclub]] and [[Gambling/Legends|gambling]] hall located in the [[Uscru Entertainment District/Legends|Uscru Entertainment District]] of Coruscant,<ref name="CSWE2">{{CSWECite|II|431|Outlander Club}}</ref> as [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] entered, [[Plot to assassinate Senator Amidala/Legends|searching]] for the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Zam Wesell/Legends|Zam Wesell]].<ref name="AoTC" />

Just stood near the entrance of the club with a drink in hand<ref name="AoTC" /> and greeted those who entered. Soon after, Just talked to Nep, Pratuhr, and Sila near the club's bar. He debated with Sila<ref name="Insider">{{InsiderCite|75|Who's Who in the Outlander Club: It's Ladies' Night}}</ref> as Skywalker walked through the club. Just watched as Wesell was disarmed by Kenobi and taken out of the club. He had [[Color/Legends|light]] skin, dark [[Hair/Legends|hair]], and wore dark colored [[Clothing/Legends|clothing]] at the club.<ref name="AoTC" />

==Behind the scenes==
{{Quote|Look for the sideburns.|Daniel Wallace|<ref name="Insider" />}}
Dixon Just first appeared in the [[2002]] [[prequel trilogy]] film [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']],<ref name="AoTC" /> where the character was portrayed by [[Justin Dix]], a member of the film's Droid Unit crew.<ref name="Insider" /> The Outlander Club scenes including Just were shot at [[Fox Studios, Sydney]] on [[July 17]], [[2000]].<ref name="Mythmaking">''[[Mythmaking: Behind the Scenes of Attack of the Clones]]''</ref> The character was first pictured when Dix, in costume, appeared in the documentary "[[Making Episode II Webdocs|A Twinkle Beyond Pluto]],"<ref name="ATBP">{{SW|url=video/a-twinkle-beyond-pluto|series=Making Episode II Webdocs|text=Part 5: A Twinkle Beyond Pluto}}</ref> released on [[July 31]], [[2001]].<ref name="ATBP Date">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/me2/archive.html|text=''Making Episode II Webdocs'' archive}}</ref> Just was first named in the article "[[Who's Who in the Outlander Club: It's Ladies' Night]]" written by [[Daniel Wallace]], which was published in the [[Star Wars Insider 75|seventy-fifth issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine<ref name="Insider" /> on [[April 6]], [[2004]].<ref name="SW.com">{{SWArchive|url=community/fanclub/mag/news20040315.html|text=The New Face of Evil}}</ref>

